160
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:35,200
Sure, they say we may not live in a condition of perfect goodness,

161
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:38,200
but we're lucky that we don't live in a condition of evil.

162
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:42,200
Our democracy is not perfect, but it's better than the bloody dictatorships.

163
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:46,200
