165
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:58,200
We kill Iraqis with our airplanes, but we don't cut their throats with machetes like they do in Rwanda, etc.

166
00:14:58,200 --> 00:15:04,200
What separates today's capitalism of a post-Soviet world is one of postmodern capitalism,

167
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:07,200
where universal values do not really exist.

168
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:11,200
There is a rejection of responsibility outside of the pursuit of capital,

169
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:15,200
