174
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:40,200
Never as an ideal for living. This is what capitalist realism is.

175
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:45,200
It is a rejection of concepts of space and time, history, everything.

176
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:50,200
Capitalist realism rejects absolutely everything except the pursuit of capital.

